{"tid":1966449,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為推 Huawei Card 實體信用卡  外型功能與 Apple Card 激似","createTime":"2020-04-10T07:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T10:04:19.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3da7ee54d62a715e6060a1eeebf6821fb6b86c60","tid":1966449,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"華為今日（9日）宣佈，於全球市場推出旗艦手機 P40 系列，同時宣佈夥拍銀聯，在中國境內市場推出 HUAWEI Card 信用卡服務。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdUQbvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdUQbvV.jpg&h=801b0b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為是次夥拍銀聯合作發行信用卡服務，以 HUAWEI Pay 為基礎，推出手機電子信用卡產品 HUAWEI Card，跟 Apple 同樣提供實體卡片與虛擬卡片兩種使用模式。<br />\n <br />\n跟 Apple Card 一樣，用戶只要直接利用手機內的錢包 APP 即可快速申請及開通，而成功開通後可同步到 HUAWEI Pay 服務。同樣，HUAWEI Card 的每筆消費都可以在錢包 App 當中查看。<br />\n <br />\n卡面與 Apple Card 一樣，僅顯示持卡人個人姓名，不過 HUAWEI Card 採用黑色配襯金色印字，更添奢華感。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/or4kyKi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2For4kyKi.jpg&h=a8bad2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\nHUAWEI Card 提供消費現金回贈、機場和高鐵等場所貴賓禮遇服務、節日消費特惠，以及華為應用 VIP 禮包等，現時申請免首年年費，惟目前只在中國境內市場推出。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：蘋果日報"},{"pid":"279936f753718b6493c56f6e66908504d571f710","tid":1966449,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:44:26.000Z","msg":"深圳新開幕Apple Store居然係賣華為手機！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1601524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1601524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"676691795e99577b848bd4610bf5721671a69452","tid":1966449,"uid":196924,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T07:45:44.000Z","msg":"芯片級安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為啲chip本身嘅安全性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13b91b3b18e6c03b9191ef38704c049cf7a023a","tid":1966449,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1